
abstract_prop p(x, y)

by commutative_prop:
    prove:
        forall x, y set:
            $p(x, y)
            =>:
                $p(y, x)
    know $p(y, x)

have a, b set

claim:
    prove:
        $p(a, b)
    know $p(b, a)

# After p is registered as commutative, known $p(b, a) verifies $p(a, b).
